The paper deals with the expressiveness of process calculi, which is a topic in the area of logic and computation (cs.LO). It also discusses encodings and name independence, which are topics in programming languages (cs.PL) and software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also mentions priority and synchronization, which are topics in formal languages and automata theory (cs.FL) and distributed computing (cs.DC), respectively.
